g.text: ACCESS PATTERNSQ1: Find information about all networks; order by name (ASC).Q2: Find the average hourly temperature within a date range for a networks sensors; order by date (DESC) and hour (DESC).Q3: Find information about all sensors in a specified network.Q4: Find raw measurements for a sensor on a given date; order by timestamp (DESC).
